criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Term;

          -  Healthy;

          -  Appropriate weight for gestational age;

          -  Infants born to mothers with otherwise healthy pregnancy and free of medications that
             impact vitamin D metabolism (except vitamin/mineral supplements) or fetal growth and
             intent to breastfeed to at least 3 months.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Preterm;

          -  Small for gestational age;

          -  Maternal smoking in pregnancy, diabetes, preeclampsia, celiac disease, inflammatory
             bowel disease and medications that impact vitamin D/mineral metabolism.
